text: Lytvensky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Alexandrovskoye Urban Settlement, Alexandrovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 419 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km south from Alexandrovsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Alexandrovsky District
title: Lytvensky
